Edition Production Notes

Some notes on production and design.

[acb]

Typography

The cover uses the font family Cyntho Pro. The regular and italic styles of
this font are freely downloadble from:

http://www.myfonts.com/fonts/konstantynov/cyntho-pro/

or

http://www.fontshop.com/fonts/downloads/mint_type/cyntho_regular_and_italic_pro/

Score

The score uses Mint Spirit from Arkandis Digital Foundry.

http://arkandis.tuxfamily.org/


Size

The edition is A3. Home printers can't bleed to the edge, so the colour
region is purposely inset by 10mm. If we print this commercially I
would prefer to bleed the colour out to the edge.








